&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Are you looking for new challenges in Data Warehousing / Business Intelligence and involvement in a range of challenging projects? Gain valuable exposure to the latest tools in the Microsoft BI platform (SQL Server, Power BI, Visual Studio etc.).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are currently expanding our Systems Development Team and recruiting to a range of technical roles. This is an exciting opportunity for talented information professionals that want to progress their career using the latest technology and join a team committed to delivering a high profile informatics change programme.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidates will need to demonstrate a clearly defined track record that includes:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;SQL development and Business Intelligence/Data Warehouse technology. Experience in the following is essential: SQL Server 2016 (T-SQL, Stored Procedures), SQL Server Reporting Services (SSRS). Experience in the following desirable: Microsoft Power BI, SQL Server Integration Services (SSIS), SQL Server Analysis Services (SSAS), and business intelligence/data warehouse technology. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
